# featureName

**Instance Property**

The name used in the model description of the CoreML model that produced this observation.

## Declaration

```swift
var featureName: String { get }
```

## Obtaining Feature Values

- **featureValue**: The feature result of a [doc://Vision/documentation/Vision/VNCoreMLRequest] that outputs neither a classification nor an image.
